data.description: This home could be just what you're looking for! 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full bathrooms, 2 car garage and 1,440 sqft all on a large lot! This home has spacious bedrooms that each have their own walk-in closets! The living room has a fireplace strategically centered on the west wall, and also features French doors leading to the back patio. The kitchen is accessible from two different directions. The HVAC and hot water tank were both replaced in 2019. The backyard features a spacious covered patio, very large backyard, shed, a fire pit with seating all around, and is fully fenced with 6' privacy. Don't miss your chance to own this house! Schedule your showings today!
